{"tid":383106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全國人大通過《國歌法》　下月1日生效】","createTime":"2017-09-01T08:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T13:25:25.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8288382ae14584f8f0946f2e858041f39d6db9","tid":383106,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"【唔好亂唱】全國人大通過《國歌法》 下月1日生效<br />\n<br />\n近日備受爭議，全國人大常委會建議在10月會議上，提請列入《基本法》附件三的《國歌法》，今日在全國人大常委會通過，規定於今年10月1日起正式實施，新法明確「侮辱國歌」的法律責任，可追究刑事責任，同時提出要在中小學應將國歌作為愛國主義教育的重要內容，鼓勵唱國歌。<br />\n<br />\n香港行政長官林鄭月娥日已經指出，在全國人大常委會通過國歌法草案後，特區政府便會展開工作，研究本地立法，她又稱《國歌法》確保國歌受到尊重，理所當然，且不屬於香港自治範圍之內，社會無需反應過敏。<br />\n<br />\n有分析指，內地通過國歌法，主要是針對香港，不少香港的示威、體育場合上都會「噓國歌」，但一直沒法被處罰，早已令內地官民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170901&amp;guid=57156566&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170901%26guid%3D57156566%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=XRlc7p3co2%2BBWC6nCTdE7aEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=471c0d76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170901%26guid%3D57156566%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=1ab7d78e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170901&amp;guid=57156566&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"9a6f9fab0eccefb85a7776f5a40090a934a583b6","tid":383106,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5980c08cb246cac464d12038fe1075f724bca4af","tid":383106,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif